quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  101,1,"Al-Qhaariqa: is Qhiyaamah ayroy sinam lubbitte meesissot taagureh migaq kinni."
  101,2,"Al-Qhaariqa is macaay?"
  101,3,"Maca koo tiysixxigee Nabiyow Al- Qhaariqa kinnim?"
  101,4,"Seehadá fíxix kee magga gibdah laahintih (ufuy mali kinnuk) innah edde gacta ayró."
  101,5,"Kaadu qaleelá fakfaken suufíh (woh illi xagooru) innah edde gacta ayró."
  101,6,"Tokkel maqaanê miidaan как yiqilseeh yan numuh tugactek."
  101,7,"Toysa usuk ruño le mano le jannatal."
  101,8,"Kaadu miidaan haliffi akak iyye numuh tu gactek;"
  101,9,"Toysa kay orbeyna haawiya deqsitta girá."
  101,10,"Maca koo tiysixxigeeh Nabiyow is kinnim?"
  101,11,"Is giray gibdi niqna íe kinni."
